# ===========================================================================
# LINE ENDING RULES - Force LF everywhere, no exceptions.
# ===========================================================================
#
# WHY: Switching between WSL and native Windows causes Git to see every file
# as modified (mode 755→644, or CRLF↔LF). The old `text=auto` rule let Git
# "guess" and it guessed wrong constantly.
#
# FIX: `eol=lf` forces LF in the working tree on ALL platforms. Modern
# Windows tools (VS Code, Node.js, Python, bash) handle LF just fine.
# The `text=auto` part still auto-detects binary files so Git won't
# corrupt images/models.
#
# The ONLY exception is .bat files, which Windows cmd.exe requires CRLF for.
# ===========================================================================

# Default: all text files use LF in working tree AND in the repo
* text=auto eol=lf

# Source code (redundant but documents intent)
*.py text eol=lf
*.ts text eol=lf
*.tsx text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.jsx text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.cjs text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.scss text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.xml text eol=lf
*.svg text eol=lf
*.env text eol=lf
*.ini text eol=lf
*.cfg text eol=lf

# Shell scripts: LF (Linux/macOS requirement)
*.sh text eol=lf

# Windows batch files: CRLF (cmd.exe requirement)
*.bat text eol=crlf

# Config files
.gitattributes text eol=lf
.gitignore text eol=lf
.gitmodules text eol=lf
.editorconfig text eol=lf
.eslintrc* text eol=lf
.prettierrc* text eol=lf
.npmrc text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
Makefile text eol=lf

# Lock files (don't mess with these)
package-lock.json text eol=lf -diff

# ===========================================================================
# BINARY FILES - Git must never touch these
# ===========================================================================

# Images
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.bmp binary
*.tiff binary

# Fonts
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary

# ML Models & Weights
*.safetensors binary
*.ckpt binary
*.pt binary
*.pth binary
*.bin binary
*.onnx binary
*.gguf binary

# Native binaries
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.node binary
*.exe binary

# Archives
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.bz2 binary
*.xz binary
*.rar binary
*.7z binary

# Other binary
*.pdf binary
*.mp4 binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
